        <short-instructions>
            <h6>Please use the following definitions to choose the most appropriate label for the given content:</h6>
            <ul>
                <li><b>News Article</b>: A passage from a complete news article.  <i>Includes: editorials, audio transcripts, obituaries, etc.</i></li>
                <li><b>Multimedia News</b>: Accompanying text to news content presented in non-text forms. <i>Includes: audio, image, and video captions, etc.</i></li>
                <li><b>Advertisement</b>: Marketing communications that promote a product, service, or idea. <i>Includes: sign-up and subscription solicitations, spam, etc.</i></li>
                <li><b>Junk Scrape</b>: Incomplete scrapes, broken content, or webpage-generated messages. <i>Includes: HTML/CSS code, error messages, login and "click to view more" instructions, etc.</i></li>
                <li><b>Personal Post</b>: Non-news content created by individual users. <i>Includes: posts or comments on blogs and forums, etc.</i></li>
                <li><b>Other</b>: Other types of non-news content. <i>Includes: weather updates, sports game score updates, copyright messages, etc.</i></li>
            </ul>
        </short-instructions>

        <!-- Use the full-instructions section for more detailed instructions that the 
